03:50.367 --> 03:54.132
Percy: SO WHAT ARE YOU
GOING TO DO NOW?

03:54.134 --> 03:58.998
NOW THAT YOU AND MAE ARE DONE,
AND SHE GOT THE HOUSE,

03:59.000 --> 04:02.265
SOME ARRANGEMENTS WERE MADE
AT SOME POINT, RIGHT?

04:02.267 --> 04:04.432
NO, NO.

04:06.700 --> 04:09.565
THE DIVORCE PAPERS LANDED
ON MY DESK YESTERDAY,

04:12.334 --> 04:18.498
AND, TO BE HONEST,
THEY'VE THROWN ME A BIT.

04:18.500 --> 04:25.798
I HEAR YOU, BUT DON'T LET THEM
SIT TOO LONG.

04:25.800 --> 04:27.132
IT'S NOT GOING TO GET
ANY EASIER,

04:27.134 --> 04:32.265
AND YOU'VE GOT
SOME LIVING TO DO.

04:32.267 --> 04:38.532
♪♪

04:38.534 --> 04:44.865
♪♪

04:44.867 --> 04:46.798
HOW'S THAT GRANDDAUGHTER
OF MINE?

04:46.800 --> 04:49.065
NOT GREAT.
I MEAN, SHE COMES HOME.

04:49.067 --> 04:50.598
SHE GOES TO HER ROOM.

04:50.600 --> 04:51.998
SHE JUST STAYS THERE.

04:52.000 --> 04:54.198
-POOR THING.
-YEAH.

04:54.200 --> 04:55.932
MAYBE I'LL GIVE HER
A VISIT.

04:55.934 --> 04:58.065
-YEAH.
-YOU KNOW, SHE DOES MISS YOU.

04:58.067 --> 04:59.865
THAT WOULD BE GREAT.
-MM-HMM.

04:59.867 --> 05:02.865
OH, YOU WANTED TO
TALK TO ME?

05:02.867 --> 05:05.065
YEAH, I DO...

05:05.067 --> 05:07.998
[ DISTANT CHATTER,
PHONE RINGS ]

05:08.000 --> 05:11.698
WELL, HOW CAN I HELP?

05:11.700 --> 05:13.198
IS IT TRUE YOU INVESTED
SOME LARGE SUM

05:13.200 --> 05:15.399
OF MONEY WITH ROCHELLE?

05:17.867 --> 05:21.398
WHO TOLD YOU THAT,
YOUR MOTHER?

05:21.400 --> 05:23.198
I ASKED HER WHATEVER HAPPENED
WITH THAT IRS BILL.

05:23.200 --> 05:27.598
SHE SAID YOU HAVE SOME PLAN
WITH ROCHELLE.

05:27.600 --> 05:29.065
YOU HAVE A PROBLEM
WITH THAT?

05:29.067 --> 05:32.198
HOW MUCH MONEY DID YOU GIVE HER?
I DIDN'T GIVE HER ANYTHING.

05:32.200 --> 05:34.032
SHE INVESTED
THE MONEY FOR ME,

05:34.034 --> 05:37.132
AND, FOR YOUR INFORMATION,
SHE DIDN'T EVEN CHARGE ME.

05:37.134 --> 05:38.831
SHE DID IT AS A FAVOR.

05:38.833 --> 05:42.132
[ Whispers ]
HOW MUCH?

05:42.134 --> 05:45.565
WHAT IS YOUR POINT
HERE, GIGI?

05:45.567 --> 05:48.465
I DON'T TRUST HER.

05:48.467 --> 05:53.532
BUT SHE'S A PART OF YOUR
LEGAL DEFENSE FUND, ISN'T SHE?

05:53.534 --> 05:55.365
YES, BUT...

05:55.367 --> 05:57.565
BUT YOU STILL
DON'T TRUST HER?

06:00.467 --> 06:02.598
DON'T LET YOUR MOTHER GET INTO
YOUR HEAD ABOUT ROCHELLE, GIGI.

06:02.600 --> 06:04.465
MNH-MNH.
SHE'S WRONG.

06:04.467 --> 06:06.798
THIS ISN'T MAMA, DADDY.

06:06.800 --> 06:10.865
THIS IS ME, AND I HAVE
MY OWN REASONS FOR ASKING.

06:12.934 --> 06:15.798
I ASSUME THAT
WHEN YOU ACCEPTED HER HELP

06:15.800 --> 06:19.431
THAT IT WAS
<i> BECAUSE</i> YOU TRUSTED HER.

06:19.433 --> 06:20.765
NO. NO.

06:20.767 --> 06:22.631
I ACCEPTED HER HELP
BECAUSE I DIDN'T TRUST HER,

06:22.633 --> 06:25.532
AND I STILL DON'T.
WHAT DOES THAT EVEN MEAN?

06:25.534 --> 06:27.665
I'M ONLY WORKING WITH HER
TO FIND OUT WHAT THE HELL

06:27.667 --> 06:30.565
SHE'S DOING IN THIS CHURCH.

06:30.567 --> 06:32.498
I AM ASTOUNDED.

06:32.500 --> 06:33.632
COME ON, DADDY.
UH-UH.

06:33.634 --> 06:36.265
DADDY, LISTEN.
NO, NO, NO.

06:36.267 --> 06:38.732
THE WAY SHE HAS JUST SWOOPED IN
AND, OUT OF THE BLUE,

06:38.734 --> 06:41.132
DROVE SOME KIND OF WEDGE
BETWEEN YOU AND MAMA...

06:41.134 --> 06:44.065
SHE DID NOTHING OF THE SORT.

06:44.067 --> 06:47.198
IT WAS YOUR MOTHER'S JEALOUSY
OVER SOMETHING INNOCENT.

06:47.200 --> 06:50.065
DADDY,
GET THAT MONEY BACK.

06:50.067 --> 06:52.931
OH, I WILL,
WITH DIVIDENDS.

06:52.933 --> 07:00.065
♪♪

07:00.067 --> 07:07.132
